---
import GiantArrowRight from "../../../SVG/GiantArrowRight.astro";
import GiantArrowLeft from "../../../SVG/GiantArrowLeft.astro";

let { header, paragraph } = Astro.props;
---

<section class="flex flex-col py-12 min-[400px]:items-center gap-y-4">
  <div class="flex text-[#2a3143] justify-center mb-3 flex-col items-center">
    <Fragment set:html={header} />
    <div class="divider"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="flex justify-center">
    <Fragment set:html={paragraph} />
  </div>
  <section class="flex py-12 items-center gap-x-2">
    <div class="grow-0">
      <GiantArrowRight styles="text-[#4e76f4]" />
    </div>
    <div class="flex flex-col grow mx-3">
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-y-2">
        <blockquote class="relative w-full px-6 py-12 shadow-decoration">
          <svg
            class="absolute -top-6 -start-8 size-16 text-gray-100 dark:text-neutral-700"
            width="16"
            height="16"
            viewBox="0 0 16 16"
            fill="none"
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            aria-hidden="true"
          >
            <path
              d="M7.39762 10.3C7.39762 11.0733 7.14888 11.7 6.6514 12.18C6.15392 12.6333 5.52552 12.86 4.76621 12.86C3.84979 12.86 3.09047 12.5533 2.48825 11.94C1.91222 11.3266 1.62421 10.4467 1.62421 9.29999C1.62421 8.07332 1.96459 6.87332 2.64535 5.69999C3.35231 4.49999 4.33418 3.55332 5.59098 2.85999L6.4943 4.25999C5.81354 4.73999 5.26369 5.27332 4.84476 5.85999C4.45201 6.44666 4.19017 7.12666 4.05926 7.89999C4.29491 7.79332 4.56983 7.73999 4.88403 7.73999C5.61716 7.73999 6.21938 7.97999 6.69067 8.45999C7.16197 8.93999 7.39762 9.55333 7.39762 10.3ZM14.6242 10.3C14.6242 11.0733 14.3755 11.7 13.878 12.18C13.3805 12.6333 12.7521 12.86 11.9928 12.86C11.0764 12.86 10.3171 12.5533 9.71484 11.94C9.13881 11.3266 8.85079 10.4467 8.85079 9.29999C8.85079 8.07332 9.19117 6.87332 9.87194 5.69999C10.5789 4.49999 11.5608 3.55332 12.8176 2.85999L13.7209 4.25999C13.0401 4.73999 12.4903 5.27332 12.0713 5.85999C11.6786 6.44666 11.4168 7.12666 11.2858 7.89999C11.5215 7.79332 11.7964 7.73999 12.1106 7.73999C12.8437 7.73999 13.446 7.97999 13.9173 8.45999C14.3886 8.93999 14.6242 9.55333 14.6242 10.3Z"
              fill="currentColor"></path>
          </svg>

          <div class="relative z-10">
            <p class="text-[#787978] font-semibold max-w-[370px]">
              <em>
                Pellentesque dictum diam. Viramus pltenibh odio cras accusamus
                citae dignissimos nulla colutpat nee, vel acelerisque
                vestibulum, integarcu lectus id maecenas.
              </em>
            </p>
          </div>
        </blockquote>
        <footer class="mt-6">
            <div class="flex">
              <div class="shrink-0">
                <img
                  class="size-16 rounded-full"
                  src="logo.webp"
                  alt="Avatar"
                />
              </div>
              <div class="ms-4">
                <div
                  class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-800 dark:text-neutral-400"
                >
                  Marina Tusa
                </div>
                <div class="text-xs text-gray-500 dark:text-neutral-500 italic">
                  Housewief
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </footer>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="grow-0">
      <GiantArrowLeft styles="text-[#4e76f4]" />
    </div>
  </section>
</section>

<style>
  .divider {
    height: 3px;
    width: 26px;
    background-color: #4e78f4;
  }

  .shadow-decoration {
    box-shadow: 0 0 12px 0px rgb(224, 224, 224);
    border-radius: 10px;
  }
</style>
